Mustafa MUHAMMAD, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Allen SELTZER and Extra Storage Space, Defendant-Respondent. C-428 September Term 2017
078839 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 13, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002275-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
